title: Sequence 2
description:
Problem Description

Write a program to input an integer N from the user and print the first N natural numbers in the following sequence:

[(1, 3), (2, 4), (5, 7), (6, 8) ....]


Input Format

A single line of input containing a single integer N


Output Format

A single line of output containing first N numbers of the given sequence.


Constraints

﻿0≤N≤1000 \le N \le 1000≤N≤100﻿



Example 1

4
[(1, 3), (2, 4), (5, 7), (6, 8)]
